::Firearm/Prowl::

Firearm drives up at full speed in front of the CF, transforming only a few 
feet from the hatch and running through. He was carrying Prowl's body, 
heading at full speed for the CR chambers. His scanners told him that Prowl 
was dying, probably too far gone for a CR.

He walks through the door of the CR room, hardly bothering to open it as he 
passes.
